    "bio": "Senior Software Engineer based in Canada. I enjoy exploring ways to integrate AI into practical life for busy families and entrepreneurs to make life easier. I publish helpful automations for free here from time to time.\n\nCurrently building:\n🗓️ ralleyreminders.com (reminder system for the forgetful/ADHD)\n👶🏻 helpbabysleep.com (baby sleep expert app to help newborn parents get more sleep)",
